    div.up1.bps-up2-3.p3
      h3.f-title.t6.pb1 Construction Components
      p.t3 Here's everything needed to build the box itself. This is the easiest section to save money in. I went with solid brass hinges and locks but you could get something from Home Depot for a lot less. Of course, some of the construction steps may change significantly if you go with different hardware. I didn't bother breaking down costs here since it will vary greatly depending on the options you pick.

      table.bom.my3
